DATABASE SETUP
=============
In file:
vim  /etc/postgresql/9.1/main/pg_hba.conf
Modify the line:
local   all             all                                     peer
to read:
local   all             all                                     md5

DATABASE Details
===============
Username: trading
Database Name: tradeDB
Password: trade

SQL Commands
============
CREATE DATABiASE tradingDB OWNER trading;
USE tradingDB;
CREATE SCHEMA trading;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE tradingdb TO trading;
